# dependency-cruiser's raw output — embeds the local machine's absolute
# `baseDir` / `rulesFile` paths in `summary.optionsUsed`, so committing it
# produces machine-specific noise and non-portable diffs. Only the
# postprocessed `dependency-previews.json` (next to it) is consumed by the
# addon at runtime; the `.raw.json` is debug output, not a deliverable.
**/.storybook/dependency-previews.raw.json
